                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The mimic is coated in an adhesive slime. Any creature that hits the mimic, is hit by the mimic, or otherwise touches the mimic must succeed at a <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"23\" data-pf2-label=\"Adhesive DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Reflex</span> save or become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Grabbed]{Grabbed} (Escape DC 23). A weapon that hits the mimic is stuck to the mimic and can be removed with a successful <span data-pf2-check=\"athletics\" data-pf2-dc=\"23\" data-pf2-label=\"Retrieve Stuck Weapon DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Athletics</span> check (made as a single action).</p>\n<p>A mimic can have any number of objects or creatures stuck to it at a time. The mimic can release a stuck creature or object by using a single action, and the adhesive dissolves 1 minute after the mimic dies, releasing all stuck objects and creatures.</p>"
                },
